Class Swrl

  • java.lang.Object
    • odase.Ontology
      • odase.w3onts.Swrl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Swrl
extends Ontology
implements Serializable
    OWL definition of the RDF Concrete Syntax for the Semantic Web Rule Language

    Generated for http://www.w3.org/2003/11/swrl.
